  <name>Cosmic Pomodoro</name>
  <summary>Simple Pomodoro applet for COSMIC Desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A minimal Pomodoro timer applet for the COSMIC desktop environment.
      Manage work and break sessions with configurable durations, session
      indicators, and automatic phase transitions with desktop notifications.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Work / break timer flow with configurable durations</li>
      <li>Start, Pause, Forward, and Restart controls</li>
      <li>Session indicators and cycle counter in the popup</li>
      <li>Panel icon with compact progress bar during sessions</li>
      <li>Desktop notifications and sound on phase transition</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
